# ==============================
# Global ignore for LoteriaApp
# ==============================

# ---------- .NET / C# ----------
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/TestResults/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates

# Rider / Visual Studio / VS Code temp
**/.idea/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode-test/

# NuGet
**/*.nupkg
**/packages/

# ---------- Angular / Node ----------
**/node_modules/
**/.angular/cache/
**/dist/
**/coverage/
**/.sass-cache/
**/tmp/
**/.cache/

# Package manager logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
